, 'To be truly great and greatly true Is to align your thoughts, words and actions in all you do', 48443, 0), (286173, 'You are not alone in this world; you are the vine from a tree that connects all mankind. Long before you were born, God wrote greatness next to your name.', 26095, 0), (286174, 'There is greatness in everyone.What is your purpose on the earth?Use your unique gifts and talent to influence mankind.', 2878, 0), (286175, 'Hmmmm...What God can''t handle doesn''t exist. Don''t limit Him with your thoughts and words.', 1313, 0), (286176, 'Tucker: "But she gave me the perfect gift."Clara: "What?"Tucker: "You.', 718, 0), (286177, 'Even when you’d lost everything you thought there was to lose, somebody came along and gave you something for free.', 24331, 0), (286178, 'Hermes''s eyes twinkled. "Martha, may I have the first package, please?"Martha opened her mouth ... and kept opening it until it was as wide as my arm. She belched out a stainless steel canister-an old-fashioned lunch box thermos with a black plastic top. The sides of the thermos were enameled with red and yellow Ancient Greek scenes-a hero killing a lion; a hero lifting up Cerberus, the three-headed dog."That''s Hercules," I said. "But how-""Never question a gift," Hermes chided. "This is a collector''s item from Hercules Busts Heads. The first season.""Hercules Busts Heads?""Great show." Hermes sighed. "Back before Hephaestus-TV was all reality programming. Of course, the thermos would be worth much more if I had the whole lunch box-', 80, 0), (286179, 'Being gifted doesn’t mean you’ve been given something. It means, you have something to give.', 323, 0), (286180, 'Practice giving things away, not just things you don''t care about, but things you do like. Remember, it is not the size of a gift, it is its quality and the amount of mental attachment you overcome that count. So don''t bankrupt yourself on a momentary positive impulse, only to regret it later. Give thought to giving. Give small things, carefully, and observe the mental processes going along with the act of releasing the little thing you liked. (53)(Quote is actually Robert A F Thurman but Huston Smith, who only wrote the introduction to my edition, seems to be given full credit for this text.)', 7993, 0), (286181, 'Gifts of the heart can''t be claimed by anyone except the giver.', 19, 0), (286182, 'The worst gift I was given is when I got out of rehab that Christmas', 48444, 0), (286183, 'The gift was not large as money goes, and my need was not great, but the spirit of the gift is beyond price and leaves me blessed and in debt.', 22, 0), (286184, 'The excellence of a gift lies in its appropriateness rather than in itsvalue.', 48445, 0), (286185, 'The great art of giving consists in this the gift should cost very little and yet be greatly coveted, so that it may be the more highly appreciated.', 1255, 0), (286186, 'I never had any doubts about my abilities. I knew I could write. I just had to figure out how to eat while doing', 548, 0), (286187, 'Gift giving is a true art.1. You need to understand the person to whom you intend to give the gift.2. You need to know what they truly want.3. You must be able to give it to them.Anything less is a symptom of varying degrees, on your part, of ignorance, distance, or i', 537, 0), (286188, 'If love is the greatest gift of all-and I believe it is- then the greatest privilege of all is to be able to love someone.', 11881, 0), (286189, 'Some men are so willing to know their future,but unwilling to face the fear of their own death.', 1296, 0), (286190, 'Gift ain''t what you take by effort, as swag ain''t what you worthy have.', 1296, 0), (286191, 'Falling in love is easy. Fools fall in love all the time. Staying in love is the test of time and the gift you give to one another daily….', 9208, 0), (286192, 'It''s so tempting to resist a little gift when you''re expecting the otherwise.', 1296, 0), (286193, 'Link says if a girl says not to get her a birthday present that means get me a birthday present and make sure it’s jewelry.', 1045, 0), (286194, 'I must indeed abide the Doom of Men whether I will or nill: the loss and the silence. But I say to you, King of the Numenoreans, not till now have I understood the tale of your people and their fall. As wicked fools I scorned them, but I pity them at last. For if this is indeed, as the Elves say, the gift of the One to Men, it is bitter to receive.', 65, 0), (286195, 'Today is a gift.Today is all I have.I be fully awake in today.', 2878, 0), (286196, 'Our flesh is a gift of laughter.', 3773, 0), (286197, 'He gave me a gift, a surprise. It was my first present in this place so far from home.', 16826, 0), (286198, 'One of the greatest gifts of life is having a chance to live as long as there are people on earth.', 30639, 0), (286199, 'While real sacrifice is committed to the result, it relishes the effort', 4397, 0), (286200, 'The gift of a new day brings with it hope and potential. It is up to you to seize it. Do you recognize what an incredible gift it is to be alive for another day? Another entire day! How will you spend it? What will you do? More importantly, what will your attitude be? How will you spend this gift? I hope you will use it wisely, with gratitude and joy in your heart. Use it to spread love and kindness, use it to make a difference, use it with joy! Carpe diem!', 6242, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (286201, 'I bought this the day before at a shopping mall. I didn''t want to forget him. Maybe I didn''t want him to forget me.', 131, 0), (286202, 'Everyone has a gift.It''s up to you to decide what you do with it.', 2876, 0), (286203, 'I made a gift for you, Good Proctor. I had to sit long hours in a chair, and passed the time with sewing." - Mary Warren', 2477, 0), (286204, 'You have given me a gift such as I never even dreamt of finding in this life.', 629, 0), (286205, 'What does not come into man''s imagination is called a "gift" because whatever passes through his imagination is in proportion to his aspiration and his worth. However, God''s gift is in proportion to God''s worth....no matter how much eyes have seen, ears heard, or minds conceived the gift you expect of Me, My gift is above and beyond all that.', 58, 0), (286206, 'I have this, this gift, I know that; and I know my obligation to it.', 77, 0), (286207, 'The greatest gifts are those that say, “I know you”.', 5117, 0), (286208, 'He created you with your special features because he was aware of your destination', 3800, 0), (286209, 'Only in a state of solitude, when you willingly stay face to face with God, can He help you to open yourself, and show the impurities preventing you from moving forward and help you to identify your unique gift, life mission and destination', 3800, 0), (286210, 'Answer the question “ what am I living for?” and become a master in this field, serve others with your gift, because you were created exactly with this goal', 3800, 0), (286211, 'Go and venture! You should not give up after failures because this gift does not belong only to you', 3800, 0), (286212, 'You are a unique individual with your own special features that you need to carry on your life mission', 3800, 0), (286213, 'To have a mission is to find your own gift', 3800, 0), (286214, 'So, each of us has a special gift and it takes time to discover it', 3800, 0), (286215, 'Reveal your gift and make it perfect', 3800, 0), (286216, 'You should not think on a small scale, you are a gift to the entire planet earth', 3800, 0), (286217, 'Develop your gift to ensure that your invention will be put into practice', 3800, 0), (286218, 'When you discover the gift inside you, you have to submit yourself to the gift and improve it', 3800, 0), (286219, 'Discover your gift if you don’t want to live the life of an ordinary person', 3800, 0), (286220, 'When you develop your gift, you will be well known', 3800, 0), (286221, 'If you can dedicate yourself to asking questions to reveal your potential, you will discover your potentials and start to fulfil your mission', 3800, 0), (286222, 'Your destination, your special gift, your personal qualities and your potential are interrelated', 3800, 0), (286223, 'Mary.” Turning at the soft sound of her name, she glanced behind herself. Then frowned. “Lassiter?” “I’m over here.” “Where?” She looked all around. “Why is your voice echoing?” “Chimney.” “What?” “I’m stuck in the fucking chimney.” She raced over to the fireplace and got on her hands and knees. Looking up into the dark flue, she shook her head. “Lass? What the hell are you doing up there?” His voice emanated from somewhere above her. “Don’t tell anyone, okay?” “What are you—” An arm came down. A very sooty arm that was encased in a red sleeve that had white trim. Or what had been white trim and which was now smudged with ash. “You’re stuck!” she exclaimed. “And thank God no one lit this fire!” “You’re telling me,” he muttered in his disembodied voice. “I had to blow out Fritz’s match like a hundred times before he gave up. Fuck, that sounds dirty. Anyway, just remind me never to try to be Santa for your kid, okay? I’m not doing this again, even for her.” Mary stretched a little farther in, but the logs on the hearth stopped her. “Lassiter. Why can’t you free yourself by dematerializing—” “I’m impaled on a hook that’s iron. I can’t go ghost. And will you just take this?” “Wha', 108, 0), (286224, 'Sow into the gift and talent God has given to you to rip an harvest', 3800, 0), (286225, 'Our life is a gift and a blessing from God', 3800, 0), (286226, 'Discover your gift and talent, then start a process of production with it if you desire to be prosperous', 3800, 0), (286227, 'Begin to increase your gift, talent, potentials, self-development if you want to be prosperous', 3800, 0), (286228, 'Until you begin to sow yourself, ability, gifts, talent into that land God has called you into, prosperity will then be yours', 3800, 0), (286229, 'Nothing like the gift of living in the present.', 4949, 0), (286230, 'Perhaps my gift to you will be as simple as a single word, whispered into your ear by one of your servants as you lie on your deathbed, a word that solves a final mystery and makes it easy for you to slip quietly into the dark.', 3795, 0), (286231, 'Having someonewho listensis a great gift,but to be truly heardis a treasure.', 30096, 0), (286232, 'The best thing to gift yourself is to be just YOURSELF, improving above the person that you were yesterday.', 11145, 0), (286233, 'It was a small tortoise with Julia’s initials set in diamonds in the living shell, and this slightly obscene object, now slipping impotently on the polished boards, now striding across the card-table, now lumbering over a rug, now withdrawn at a touch, now stretching its neck and swaying its withered, antediluvian head, became a memorable part of the evening, one of those needlehooks of experience which catch the attention when larger matters are at stake.', 399, 0), (286234, 'Live Life. Fight for life. Every day is a gift. Don’t take it for granted.In memory of Carter Desmond McFillin.', 8446, 0), (286235, 'I have diligently disciplined my life to search out life’s gifts in the very places where society mistakenly says life stores its scraps. And I am constantly amazed that in the treasure trove that surrounds me, I stand in the company of so few.', 4397, 0), (286236, 'Sincere doubts, handled properly, can become a gift.', 3962, 0), (286237, 'We have errantly romanticized love as something we freely get verses something we sacrifice for in the giving.', 4397, 0), (286238, 'Maybe a holiday miracle will change Mearth’s awful behavior,” Mandy suggested with optimism.“The only holiday miracle around here is that Mearth hasn’t murdered us both yet,” said Alecto, lighting another cigarette, his hands shaking erratically. He looked exhausted and terrified, his gray eyes soulless.“Do you know what Mearth likes, Alecto?” Mandy questioned.“Vegetables, she likes celery a lot, and lettuce,” Alecto responded in a quiet monotone. “I don’t know what else she likes. I’ve never asked her.”“Well, she has to like something… doesn’t everyone?”“Not her, Mandy Valems.', 4547, 0), (286239, 'Time'' is actually the best gift, given to us by our Creator.', 11007, 0), (286240, 'If God give you strength and courage, don''t use it to intimidate people or overpower them, rather use your gift to help others find their own way to strength.', 3341, 0), (286241, 'Be your own kind of brave.', 7514, 0), (286242, 'Some days are better than others. The same can be said about people.', 4616, 0), (286243, 'The gift is you.', 10589, 0), (286244, 'The present: It is interesting that the “NOW" is called "the present.” The present is the ultimate gift; it is the gift of truth and life. You are given the present every second, and you will receive it forever. The present is the only thing that exists, the only thing you are ever conscious of. Your life is a series of presents moving through time. The future does not exist until it becomes the present.Life is one perpetual present.Creation is happening now: Your body, mind, and the world around it are being created from microsecond to microsecond. Things may look the same, but they are not; everything is constantly changing and being recreated. Our life and our world is being created 