rget it never', 2586, 0), (286277, 'The greatest investment in life is the investment of unconditional love, as a profit you will get the greatest gift of life: happiness.', 2586, 0), (286278, 'Plant the trees just for beauty,If flowers bloom or fruits ripen, Enjoy it as a gift and appreciate nature as a universal giver.', 2586, 0), (286279, 'For my first recital ever, they gave me a cello. And for this one, they gave me you.', 150, 0), (286280, 'Your Temporary Santa, "He says presents aren''t important, but I think they are- not because of how much they cost, but for the opportunity they provide to say ''I understand you.', 251, 0), (286281, 'Life is a wave of love for a lover, a gift for a giver, a drama for an actor, and a canvas for a painter.', 2586, 0), (286282, 'I discovered that the real meaning of Christmas has nothing to do with you at all. It is about a very special gift. I want to you tell you about this gift.', 24623, 0), (286283, 'You are a gift. You are the only one of you on this planet and God made you specifically to deliver that gift to mankind. I request that you stop waiting to remember what you are here for and start sharing you gift with the world.', 5356, 0), (286284, 'She’d never felt more alone, even as hundreds of people walked by. No one recognized her, and she began to treasure her anonymity as a gift.', 7173, 0), (286285, 'Life is a gift. Regard it as such. Return the blessing through each life you touch. Every seed planted, springs forth new birth. Allow your bouquet to cover the earth.', 18975, 0), (286286, 'Blessing is essentially the transformative experience of knowing and honoring God as the Giver', 48450, 0), (286287, 'If stupidity were a gift, only a few would have it.', 4238, 0), (286288, 'When someone tells you a piece of their life, they’re giving you a gift, not granting you your due.', 313, 0), (286289, 'Don''t give a gift with the expectation to get,but if you have a gift, always try to give.', 2586, 0), (286290, 'Glory is